<br>
“That also,” Tor agreed.  He motioned with his head toward the part of the forest where the natural warm springs lay.  “Go on.  I’ll inform father as to the reason for your delay.”  Alexander gave him a curt nod and turned his horse back around to head toward the bathing pools.  <br>
