<br>
“What have I done to offend you so, your highness?”<br>
<br>
Chloe arched an eyebrow.<br>
<br>
“Well, gee.  I don’t know,” she said sarcastically.  “But I’m pretty sure it had something to do with you watching me take a bath without me knowing you were there.”<br>
<br>
