<br>
Alexander was surprised that the thought of not taking over the Sullivan kingdom didn’t bother him as much as it would have before he met Chloe; but now he just wanted her.  He could inherit his own father’s throne and they could remain there for all he cared.  He just wanted her with him.<br>
