<br>
“I have tried to tell him through his dreams that you will not be returning,” James said and turned his back to them.<br>
<br>
“What?!  How could you ---” she stopped talking as she saw James’s hands raise to the sides of his head and he let out a small whimpering sound in pain.<br>
<br>
