<br>
Alexander seemed taken aback by all of the information he had been forced to absorb in such a short period of time, but he managed a nod.<br>
<br>
“And Lucas?” he asked.  James turned his back on them once again and walked over to stare out the window.<br>
<br>
“It is unseen.”<br>
