<br>
“Mr. Luthor?  Sir?”<br>
<br>
Lex shook his head, his body shuddering a little as he was jerked from the strange daydream/vision/fantasy thing he had been having.  He didn’t even realize that Tom Yager, the man he had called in to take over the shift Gabe had been working, had been calling his name for the last few minutes to get his attention.  <br>
<br>
